        "body": "Previous Work by @Shamli-Singh-Yadav:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/088f601a-6783-41d8-a5e8-b8b968128a5d\r\n\r\nMy Improved Version:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3bce35c1-9ce2-4255-a9bf-8411261c5723\r\n\r\nDescription:\r\n\r\nThis PR revamps the Author Page (Author-page.html) with a modern and visually refined layout.\r\nThe new design focuses on better structure, responsiveness, and readability.\r\n\r\nKey Improvements:\r\n\r\nEnhanced hero section with better typography and CTA\r\n\r\nOrganized genre cards with icons and subtle hover effects\r\n\r\nClean author grid showcasing images, bios, and genres\r\n\r\nAdded smooth spacing, shadows, and rounded corners for modern aesthetics\r\n\r\nRefined contact section with improved alignment and usability\r\n\r\nConsistent color palette and improved visual hierarchy\r\n\r\nOverall, this update transforms the page into a more professional, elegant, and user-friendly interface while keeping the core theme intact.",
